We may want to enumerate items within a paragraph to
\begin{enumerate*}[label=(\alph*)]
  \item save space  \item make a less prominent statement,
  or \item for some other reason.  \end{enumerate*}

As before we can continue the list
\begin{enumerate*}[resume*]
 \item with the key \texttt{resume} \item or with
 \texttt{resume*} \item or apply some other  \par  change.
\end{enumerate*}
\textbf{Paragraph breaks are ignored in such lists!}
